column5: I'll probably be one of the last lo leave for the Bay later today so if any of you have any messages for the troops in general or for a specific person, post them here please. I will print them out around 4PM and deliver them tonight.  tanks.
4pm is still earlier than me.. i'm stuck pushing a pencil until 5pm..
I'll make sure I bring any messages with me.  I'm here till about 2 pm tomorrow  . See you there.

Yes,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,, Can you please make sure my little buddy Terry, has a dry change of cloths.Also tell Wayne,Im flying his plane.Dont want them to sit to long and sieze up.  HAVE FUN AND HAVE A SAFE DRIVE MY FRIENDS
Pictures! Reports! I need something to read.
What ever "bump" happens in BOQ stays at BOQ.
Roy you can tell dawg that if he needs to make a stop to just call me, he's got my number.  Good luck to you and everyone else and be safe!  Cheers!

Hey Roy,  I'll be trying to make the trip up Sunday morning. Hopefully with a couple of other (non-OFNrs) with a boat. If not I'll make the trip myself and hope someone will have a spot on their boat still open.  Thanks,  Stan (HearingFish)
Ok folks, printing this and leaving. All y'all have a great weekend!  Good Night Mrs. Calabash wherever y'are.
